extends layout

block content
  h1 FreeCodeCamp API Basejump: File Metadata Microservice
  br
  h3 User stories:
  p I can submit a FormData object that includes a file upload.
  p When I submit something, I will receive the file size in bytes within the JSON response
  br
  h3 Example usage:
  p Just upload a small file and you receive the filesize in bytes.
  h3 Example output:
  code { "filesize": "99226 bytes" }
  br
  br
  form(action='/fileupload', enctype="multipart/form-data", method="post")
    input(type="file", name="file" required)
    input(type="submit" value="upload")


